002package com.commercetools.api.models.type;
003
004import java.time.LocalDate;
005import java.time.LocalTime;
006import java.time.ZonedDateTime;
007import java.time.format.DateTimeFormatter;
008import java.util.Collections;
009import java.util.List;
010import java.util.Map;
011import java.util.Optional;
012import java.util.stream.Collectors;
013
014import javax.annotation.Nullable;
015
016import com.commercetools.api.models.MapAccessor;
017import com.commercetools.api.models.common.LocalizedString;
018import com.commercetools.api.models.common.Money;
019import com.commercetools.api.models.common.Reference;
020import com.commercetools.api.models.common.TypedMoney;
021
022/**
023 * Accessor for retrieving type safe custom field values
024 */
025public class CustomFieldsAccessor extends MapAccessor<Object> {
026    private final Map<String, Object> values;
027
028    public CustomFieldsAccessor(CustomFields customFields) {
029        super(Optional.ofNullable(customFields.getFields()).map(FieldContainer::values).orElse(Collections.emptyMap()));
030        this.values = Optional.ofNullable(customFields.getFields())
031                .map(FieldContainer::values)
032                .orElse(Collections.emptyMap());
033    }
034
035    public CustomFieldsAccessor(FieldContainer fieldContainer) {
036        super(fieldContainer.values());
037        this.values = fieldContainer.values();
038    }
039
040    @Nullable
041    public LocalDate asDate(final String field) {
042        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsDate);
043    }
044
045    @Nullable
046    public LocalTime asTime(final String field) {
047        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsTime);
048    }
049
050    @Nullable
051    public ZonedDateTime asDateTime(final String field) {
052        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsDateTime);
053    }
054
055    @Nullable
056    public List<LocalDate> asSetDate(final String field) {
057        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetDate);
058    }
059
060    @Nullable
061    public List<LocalTime> asSetTime(final String field) {
062        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetTime);
063    }
064
065    @Nullable
066    public List<ZonedDateTime> asSetDateTime(final String field) {
067        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetDateTime);
068    }
069
070    @Nullable
071    public String asString(final String field) {
072        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsString);
073    }
074
075    @Nullable
076    public Boolean asBoolean(final String field) {
077        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsBoolean);
078    }
079
080    @Nullable
081    public Double asDouble(final String field) {
082        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsDouble);
083    }
084
085    @Nullable
086    public LocalizedString asLocalizedString(final String field) {
087        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsLocalizedString);
088    }
089
090    @Nullable
091    public CustomFieldEnumValue asEnum(final String field) {
092        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsEnum);
093    }
094
095    @Nullable
096    public CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue asLocalizedEnum(final String field) {
097        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsLocalizedEnum);
098    }
099
100    @Nullable
101    public Long asLong(final String field) {
102        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsLong);
103    }
104
105    @Nullable
106    public Reference asReference(final String field) {
107        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsReference);
108    }
109
110    @Nullable
111    public TypedMoney asMoney(final String field) {
112        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsMoney);
113    }
114
115    @Nullable
116    public List<String> asSetString(final String field) {
117        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetString);
118    }
119
120    @Nullable
121    public List<Boolean> asSetBoolean(final String field) {
122        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetBoolean);
123    }
124
125    @Nullable
126    public List<Double> asSetDouble(final String field) {
127        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetDouble);
128    }
129
130    @Nullable
131    public List<LocalizedString> asSetLocalizedString(final String field) {
132        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetLocalizedString);
133    }
134
135    @Nullable
136    public List<CustomFieldEnumValue> asSetEnum(final String field) {
137        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetEnum);
138    }
139
140    @Nullable
141    public List<CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue> asSetLocalizedEnum(final String field) {
142        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetLocalizedEnum);
143    }
144
145    @Nullable
146    public List<Long> asSetLong(final String field) {
147        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetLong);
148    }
149
150    @Nullable
151    public List<Reference> asSetReference(final String field) {
152        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetReference);
153    }
154
155    @Nullable
156    public List<Money> asSetMoney(final String field) {
157        return get(field, CustomFieldsAccessor::mapAsSetMoney);
158    }
159
160    private static LocalDate mapAsDate(final Object value) {
161        if (value instanceof LocalDate) {
162            return (LocalDate) value;
163        }
164        return LocalDate.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_LOCAL_DATE);
165    }
166
167    private static LocalTime mapAsTime(final Object value) {
168        if (value instanceof LocalTime) {
169            return (LocalTime) value;
170        }
171        return LocalTime.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_LOCAL_TIME);
172    }
173
174    private static ZonedDateTime mapAsDateTime(final Object value) {
175        if (value instanceof ZonedDateTime) {
176            return (ZonedDateTime) value;
177        }
178        return ZonedDateTime.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_ZONED_DATE_TIME);
179    }
180
181    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
182    private static List<LocalDate> mapAsSetDate(final Object listValue) {
183        return ((List<Object>) listValue).stream().map(value -> {
184            if (value instanceof LocalDate) {
185                return (LocalDate) value;
186            }
187            return LocalDate.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_LOCAL_DATE);
188        }).collect(Collectors.toList());
189    }
190
191    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
192    private static List<LocalTime> mapAsSetTime(final Object listValue) {
193        return ((List<Object>) listValue).stream().map(value -> {
194            if (value instanceof LocalTime) {
195                return (LocalTime) value;
196            }
197            return LocalTime.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_LOCAL_TIME);
198        }).collect(Collectors.toList());
199    }
200
201    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
202    private static List<ZonedDateTime> mapAsSetDateTime(final Object listValue) {
203        return ((List<Object>) listValue).stream().map(value -> {
204            if (value instanceof ZonedDateTime) {
205                return (ZonedDateTime) value;
206            }
207            return ZonedDateTime.parse((String) value, DateTimeFormatter.ISO_ZONED_DATE_TIME);
208        }).collect(Collectors.toList());
209    }
210
211    private static String mapAsString(final Object value) {
212        return (String) value;
213    }
214
215    private static Boolean mapAsBoolean(final Object value) {
216        return (Boolean) value;
217    }
218
219    private static Double mapAsDouble(final Object value) {
220        return (Double) value;
221    }
222
223    private static LocalizedString mapAsLocalizedString(final Object value) {
224        return (LocalizedString) value;
225    }
226
227    private static CustomFieldEnumValue mapAsEnum(final Object value) {
228        return (CustomFieldEnumValue) value;
229    }
230
231    private static CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue mapAsLocalizedEnum(final Object value) {
232        return (CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue) value;
233    }
234
235    private static Long mapAsLong(final Object value) {
236        return (Long) value;
237    }
238
239    private static Reference mapAsReference(final Object value) {
240        return (Reference) value;
241    }
242
243    private static TypedMoney mapAsMoney(final Object value) {
244        return (TypedMoney) value;
245    }
246
247    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
248    private static List<String> mapAsSetString(final Object listValue) {
249        return (List<String>) listValue;
250    }
251
252    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
253    private static List<Boolean> mapAsSetBoolean(final Object listValue) {

255    }
256

265    }
266
267    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
268    private static List<CustomFieldEnumValue> mapAsSetEnum(final Object listValue) {
269        return (List<CustomFieldEnumValue>) listValue;
270    }
271
272    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
273    private static List<CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue> mapAsSetLocalizedEnum(final Object listValue) {
274        return (List<CustomFieldLocalizedEnumValue>) listValue;
275    }
276
277    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
278    private static List<Long> mapAsSetLong(final Object listValue) {
279        return (List<Long>) listValue;
280    }
281
282    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
283    private static List<Reference> mapAsSetReference(final Object listValue) {
284        return (List<Reference>) listValue;
285    }

287    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")

290    }
